## About

TiddlyWiki is a unique non-linear notebook for capturing, organizing, and sharing complex information.

This add-on launches a self-contained TiddlyWiki server within your Home Assistant OS instance, giving you a local or remote-accessible personal wiki or knowledge base.

## Key Features

- 🌐 Full-featured TiddlyWiki (Node.js edition)
- 🔁 Persistent storage for your wiki content
- ⚙️ Configurable startup arguments
- 📁 Integrated with Home Assistant add-on data storage
- 🖥️ Simple Web UI access

